---
// Skip to Main Content Link for Screen Readers
---

<a
  href="#main-content"
  class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 bg-primary-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md z-50 transition-all duration-200"
  aria-label="Skip to main content"
>
  Skip to main content
</a>

<style>
  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  .focus\:not-sr-only:focus {
    position: static;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    overflow: visible;
    clip: auto;
    white-space: normal;
  }
</style>
